Subject: Require Description/ Classification details of output from the AD Reports.
Description:
Regarding the AD Reports that are generated from the AD scan, we would like information on the definition of some of the output.
Below are some examples of the type of information we require:

1. On All Audited Domains- what are users - what exactly does this cover , is it all account types ?   - a, -o etc
2. Exception Summary -  need to know the criteria/description of these fields within  this summary  - example what constitutes a stale user? 
3.Group membership Details - what's classed as other?
4. Privileged Group Membership - why the ‘Other’ data is not populated as ‘User’, ‘Group’ or ‘Computer’ ?
What_We_Know__c: Most of this infromation is available in Helpcenter
Solution_Comment__c: Explained the terms according to an article: https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Solutions/ActiveDirectoryInventory/3-AD_Exceptions.htm
